# GitHub personal access token (read-only scope is fine).
# Used by the Lucide ingestion fetcher to avoid the unauthenticated rate limit
# of 60 requests/hour. Without a token, ingestion may still work but flakily.
#
# Generate at https://github.com/settings/tokens — no scopes required for public repos.
#
# Vercel: set this in Project Settings → Environment Variables
# GitHub Actions: not needed (the workflow uses GITHUB_TOKEN automatically)
GITHUB_TOKEN=
